title: Michael Lealamanua
text: I have ordered an intake kit for my 2007 Nissan Versa online. Soon my order was shipped and a tracking number was sent to me through email. My kit arrived fast and was packed well. The kit included everything I needed for the install. Now my car isn't boring to drive and sounds great and is a joy to drive . Thank you Pro Import Tuners for the excellent product!
